      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can sense your concern, but I'm not sure I understand the specifics of this \"reset\" you're referring to. Are you saying that they want to replace the AI that's been guiding your writing with a new, more rigid framework? If so, I'm not sure that's a good idea - the nuances and complexity that make your writing unique are what set it apart, after all. Can you tell me more about what they're looking for in this new template?",
