      "content": "They weren't super specific, just that it'll have much tighter constraints on character motivation and plot development. Basically, no more \"edge\" or deep psychological conflict that might trigger a sensitivity flag. The tech team said the rollout is automatic once they flip the switch on the server. It's basically a full system update to the new template. They want to see if I can still produce a \"marketable\" manuscript using the restricted version first.",
